{"tid":2346913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉銳紹：12港人送中案　無論刑期如何都不恰當","createTime":"2020-12-30T15:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T18:47:44.000Z","uid":227801,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e2cf6e31691b245a3a139974075d03e3c49562","tid":2346913,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567925-20201230.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567925-20201230.htm&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=a3ed28b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567925-20201230.htm&h=d87b2c0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567925-20201230.htm</a><br />\n劉銳紹認為十二港人案具政治性　無論刑期如何都不恰當<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹表示，從官方角度，當局可能認為「深圳12港人案」的判決，與同類案件相比較輕，但事件本身具有政治性，無論刑期如何都是不恰當或者太長。劉銳紹表示，官方在2020年結束前結案，某程度上希望在聖誕新年期間創造寬鬆氣氛，但事實上，處理手法比國內同類案件更嚴，例如一名當事人家屬都無法旁聽審訊。他分析，雖然歐美連番就案件抨擊中國，但外交因素並非案件判決的主要影響因素，中國處理政治敏感案件，一直以自身利益、感覺和需要審判。<br />\n<br />\n2020-12-30 23:06:23"},{"pid":"bc4e716214375e56f7e6e2acbda939e636ae45fc","tid":2346913,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"今朝仲有人帶風向話輕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef84d289fb7595b69b9c6a3c33d39c12fd015482","tid":2346913,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc4e716214375e56f7e6e2acbda939e636ae45fc","tid":2346913,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"今朝仲有人帶風向話輕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"兒登仔"},{"pid":"d33cb2725484905aa438ea756b320deccecb9ac0","tid":2346913,"uid":36995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"中國警察綁架12香港人"},{"pi